body_html: @aimhabo can you please inspect or post the file that generated the "#error This file was generated by an older version of protoc which is" message? I'd expect the protobuf version in that number to be <3.6.1, which means that either that file is lying around from a previous build, or you still have mixed protobuf versions somewhere on your system.
